<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
  <h1 style="color: #28a745;">Fast Queries Page</h1>
  <p>This page executes minimal database operations for fast response times.</p>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px;">
    
    <section style="border: 1px solid #28a745; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #d4edda;">
      <h3>Quick Counts</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Total Users:</strong> <%= @total_users %></li>
        <li><strong>Total Posts:</strong> <%= @total_posts %></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="border: 1px solid #28a745; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #d4edda;">
      <h3>Latest Post</h3>
      <% if @latest_post %>
        <p><strong><%= @latest_post.title %></strong></p>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
          By <%= @latest_post.user&.name || 'Unknown' %> • <%= time_ago_in_words(@latest_post.created_at) %> ago
        </p>
      <% else %>
        <p>No posts found.</p>
      <% end %>
    </section>

    <section style="border: 1px solid #28a745; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #d4edda;">
      <h3>Performance Info</h3>
      <p>✅ Fast database queries</p>
      <p>✅ Minimal processing time</p>
      <p>✅ Quick response expected</p>
    </section>

  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h3>About This Page</h3>
    <p>
      This page demonstrates <strong>fast queries</strong> including simple COUNT operations and basic record retrieval.
      It should generate minimal database load and fast response times in Rails Pulse monitoring.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>